The workshop will be a forum for researchers , developers and users of Hypertext / WWW and Multimedia technologies in environment protection and other environmentally-related areas . The workshop is supported by the German Computer Society GI ( Gesellschaft fuer Informatik ) , special interest groups 4 . 6 . 1 ( Informatics in Environment Protection ) and 4 . 9 . 1 ( Hypertext Systems ) . The conference language will be German , but submissions of presentations in English will be also admitted . The deadline for submissions is January 15 , 1998 .
